						               													<description>You have been reincarnated in this multidimensional realm as a travel writer. You and your fellow passengers ride on the Black Comet, an inter-dimensional railroad that connects all worlds.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;We will survey sightseeing attractions and interview passengers to write travel articles. The reporter who publishes the most travel articles will make a name for themselves in this world.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In &amp;#231;&amp;#149;&amp;#176;&amp;#231;&amp;#149;&amp;#140;/&amp;#229;&amp;#162;&amp;#131;&amp;#231;&amp;#149;&amp;#140;/&amp;#233;&amp;#137;&amp;#132;&amp;#233;&amp;#129;&amp;#147;&amp;#230;&amp;#151;&amp;#133;&amp;#232;&amp;#161;&amp;#140; (Another World / Another Realm / Rail Travel), you bid on passengers who appear each round using your dice. Not only do you have to outbid your opponents, you want enough dice to make a successful roll to acquire the passenger&amp;rsquo;s sightseeing cards. You also compete with other players for souvenirs. Specific sets of cards are used to publish articles, the main source of points at the end of the game. You can earn additional points for each passenger card you acquire, and some passengers earn bonus points with specific articles. After 5 rounds, the player with the most points is the winner.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game features a beautifully illustrated cast of characters riding on the Black Comet. All of the passenger, sightseeing, and souvenir cards are unique, with imaginative text that hints at a bigger story. Among the original ideas are references to folklore and popular media. This is a game with high production values, great art, and fun gameplay.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
